data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in San Tan Valley, located in the highly sought-after Circle Cross Ranch community. This stunning property features 4 bedrooms plus a den, 3 bathrooms, and a refreshing pool, on a premium 8,000sqft+ lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-designed floorplan that maximizes space and functionality. The open great room and formal dining room create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is gorgeous boasting stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, rich cabinetry with stylish hardware, a beautiful backsplash, and a spacious kitchen island with a convenient breakfast bar. The great room features an accent wall, a modern ceiling fan, and a sliding French glass door that opens up to the resort-style backyard, allowing for seamless indoor-outdoor living. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, offering ample space, natural light, and an ensuite bathroom. The ensuite bathroom features a dual sink vanity, a separate shower and bathtub, and a massive walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are spotless and neutral in decor, creating a versatile canvas for your personal touch. Bedroom 2 has an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet, making it a perfect luxurious guest suite. The backyard is nothing short of a desert oasis, featuring a sparkling swimming pool with a delightful water feature. A covered patio provides shade and comfort, and a pergola with a paved floor offers an inviting spot for outdoor dining, lounging, or entertaining. With this backyard, you'll have your own private paradise right at home. This rare find of a home offers a perfect blend of style, functionality, and outdoor luxury. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and start living the Arizona dream.

Circle Cross Ranch is in a perfect San Tan Valley Location close to shopping, dining, golf, entertainment, and much more!
